UID:10000510-1775210400-1775237400@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Help Frenzy Coffee celebrate their 1st full year in Davis! \nC
 ome join the fun at this all-day birthday party featuring live DJ sets and
  a variety of local vendors. Whether you’re grabbing your morning coffee
 \, stopping by for lunch\, or hanging out in the afternoon\, there will be
  great music\, good vibes\, and plenty of ways to celebrate with the commu
 nity. \nBring your friends\, family\, or coworkers and enjoy the lively at
 mosphere right in the heart of downtown Davis. Everyone is welcome! \nFree
  to attend – no tickets needed. Just stop by\, enjoy the music\, shop lo
 cal vendors\, and help celebrate one year of Frenzy Coffee! \nDate/Time: F
 riday\, April 3\, 2026 | 10:00 AM – 5:30 PM \nLocation: Frenzy Coffee\, 
 305 1st Street\, Downtown Davis
LOCATION:Frenzy Coffee\, 305 1st St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
