DESCRIPTION:Philippine Culture Night 38 is Mga Kaibigan's 38th annual cult
 ural show. This event has components like Philippine cultural dances\, mod
 ern dances\, and a play in a 2-hour-long showcase. The purpose of the even
 t is to celebrate Pilipinx culture and tell Pilipinx-American stories to a
  general audience. Our shows on April 11th 6-8PM\, April 12th 12-2PM\, and
  April 12th 6-8PM will be open to the general public\, but will be tickete
 d.
