DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260413T200000
UID:2464d607046f81964679c85e117b99e9@events.yolocountylibrary.org
DESCRIPTION:Davis Makerspace is a community workspace for makers and build
 ers\, designers and inventors. A small assortment of tools will be availab
 le for use and staff or volunteers will be on hand to provide some assista
 nce. Supervised children are welcome. Participants must provide a signed l
