UID:10004167-1776499200-1776517200@visityolo.com
SUMMARY:Davis Farmers Market
DESCRIPTION:Year-round at Central Park in downtown Davis\, thousands gather each week to shop for what is grown\, raised\, and made locally at our markets. We are dedicated to bringing farmers right to your table\, so we stay open rain or shine. \nWalk rows of stalls lined with an array of fruits and vegetables\, including certified organic produce\, choice meats\, chicken\, seafood\, wine\, local eggs and honey. Choose from a variety of fresh-baked goods\, plants\, flowers and gifts. Enjoy a picnic from one of our many food stands\, made from market ingredients.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/davis-farmers-market-2/2026-04-18/
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Small_CapayCarrots-002.jpg
END:VEVENT
