X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Yolo Library": "https://events.yolocountylibrary.org/event/16367781"}
X-SOURCE-ID:yolo_library
SUMMARY:Healthy Heroes with RIVER Clinic  (Davis)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T150000
UID:6beeb1b76b6a809c619508e5045a33f3@events.yolocountylibrary.org
DESCRIPTION:Join the RIVER clinic interns for a series of fun healthy livi
 ng activities! Complete your “superhero training” certificate by visit
 ing all five of our stations with a focus on nutrition\, healthy eating\, 
 and exercise! Activities include a trivia wheel for healthy facts\, creati
 ng colorful nutrition bracelets\, decorating exercise-dice\, a healthy lun
 ch sorting game\, and making your own superfood superhero!  \n\nRIVER Pe
 diatric Clinic is a student-run free clinic based in partnership with UC D
 avis School of Medicine. As a part of our mission to improve the health of
  the pediatric population of the greater Sacramento area\, we provide heal
 th education activities developed and delivered by our interns.
LOCATION:Blanchard Room\, Mary L Stephens Davis Branch Library
URL:https://events.yolocountylibrary.org/event/16367781
X-SOURCE:Yolo Library
END:VEVENT
