DESCRIPTION:For the event\, we would like to host our annual Synthesis Dan
 ce Showcase. This event is rooted in promoting our values of platforming t
 he local dance community by allowing any person\, group\, or organization 
 to choreograph and perform a piece for the Davis community. This will invo
 lve working alongside individuals or organizations that are affiliated wit
 h UC Davis\, and those that are not. Also\, this will be a ticketed event 
 that is open to the general public.
